remarks.p:
Notes:


Submit can be canceled by oEvent.cancel=true;

Response can be canceled by oEvent.cancelResponse=true;

Full postback can be triggered by oEvent.fullPostBack=true;

ul.li:
The  property can be used to apply more custom
            html styles while rendering.

            Examples:



            UltraWebTab1.CustomRules = "background-image:url(./myImage.gif); background-repeat:no-repeat;";

            UltraWebTab1.CustomRules = "padding:10";

            UltraWebTab1.CustomRules = "cursor:default; padding-left:10; padding-right:20";

remarks.p:
TextBox txtInput = new TextBox();

            txtInput.Width = Unit.Pixel(190);

            UltraWebTab1.Tabs.GetTab(0).ContentPane.Children.Add(txtInput);

            Infragistics.WebUI.UltraWebTab.Tab t;

            Infragistics.WebUI.UltraWebTab.TabSeparator ts;

            if (UltraWebTab1.Tabs[0].GetType().Equals(typeof(Infragistics.WebUI.UltraWebTab.Tab)))

t = (Infragistics.WebUI.UltraWebTab.Tab)UltraWebTab1.Tabs[0];
            else

ts = (Infragistics.WebUI.UltraWebTab.TabSeparator)UltraWebTab1.Tabs[0];

UltraWebTab1.CustomRules = "background-image:url(./myImage.gif); background-repeat:no-repeat;";

UltraWebTab1.CustomRules = "padding:10";

UltraWebTab1.CustomRules = "cursor:default; padding-left:10; padding-right:20";
